txt.en: The hounds of the Corsairs have been caged in one home in Lothgobel, and they are filthy, vicious mongrels who hunger for death.
Hounds can be found in a home in Lothgobel in central Lamedon.\n\nYou should defeat hounds in Lothgobel.
